pageContext.claim: “'Congressman Schiff omitted and distorted key facts' @FoxNews So, what else is new. He is a total phony!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump in this case actually misquotes Molly Line, a Fox News host, who had reported: "Congressman Schiff, he argues the Republican memo 'omitted and distorted key facts.'" The host was not being critical of Rep. Adam Schiff (D-Calif.)
